  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In [SALTED], you become bacon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why bacon? Why climb? It doesn't matter. Just climb what's in front of you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag your mouse to adjust the power and send the bacon flying. That's all it takes. Can you overcome this challenge? We look forward to your challenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639420/extras/03706ef0919550e8270233cb3762acbe.avif?t=1745952555\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639420/extras_big/03706ef0919550e8270233cb3762acbe.avif?t=1745952555 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was created with influences from \"Getting Over It with Bennet Foddy\" and \"Jump King.\"</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In [SALTED], you become bacon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why bacon? Why climb? It doesn't matter. Just climb what's in front of you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag your mouse to adjust the power and send the bacon flying. That's all it takes. Can you overcome this challenge? We look forward to your challenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639420/extras/03706ef0919550e8270233cb3762acbe.avif?t=1745952555\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639420/extras_big/03706ef0919550e8270233cb3762acbe.avif?t=1745952555 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was created with influences from \"Getting Over It with Bennet Foddy\" and \"Jump King.\"</p>",
